                  "content": "She should work to better understand the disorder that she is treating."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_2",
                  "content": "She should be more confrontational in her approach so as to make clients aware of their difficulties."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_3",
